    "Reappraisal Specificity -\"This rethinking is specific to the following scenario (as opposed to being able to fit lots of different scenarios).\"",
    "Given that no such evaluation has been made, we could not use existing measures.",
    "We therefore chose these four dimensions based on aspects of reappraisals evaluated in the literature.",
    "Potential moderators.",
    "After completing the study, participants filled out a few surveys that served as potential moderators for the effect."
